    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change law so people over 16 get a whole life term if they commit knife crime",
        "additional_details": "We feel the UK has been blighted by murders of children committed by children or young adults. One knife death is one too many.",
        "background": "We think that action on knife crime has to be taken. We want the government to introduce stronger sentencing for carrying weapon without a lawful excuse and for offenders over 16 to receive a mandatory whole life term.",
